scenes.description: Showcase of Gura's Shoulder Bag merchandise.
Showcase of Amelia Watson's Private Investigator Cap merchandise.
Announcement of the 3D Acrylic Stands merchandise.
Members showing individual acrylic stands and posing like them.
The group shares their feelings about the collaboration and has a group hug.
Members discuss audience comments and tease upcoming performances.
The members head towards the stage area.
Loading screen transitioning to the performance stage.
